title: Silky Van Gogh Amandiers Scarf
description:
Inspired by Van Gogh’s Almond Blossom painting, this silk scarf will make a great accessory for any wardrobe. Wear this scarf traditionally around your neck, or tie a bow around your wrist for a playful look. Don’t be afraid to tie it around your handbag for a fun pop of color!

Details:

• 100% Silk

• Made in France

• 2.75x 40 inches
